        <abstract>
            <para>The Pullen Herbarium (MISS) collection is located on the campus of the University of Mississippi in Oxford, MS, and consists of over 80,000 vascular plant specimens, as well as non vascular plants, slime molds and macrofungi.&amp;nbsp; With funding from the National Science Foundation, the collection is housed in a compactor system and the specimen data and images have been digitized.&amp;nbsp; Vascular plant specimens can be searched on SERNEC and macrofungi are displayed in MycoPortal.</para>
        </abstract>
